   - **`app/src/renderer/src/screens/BranchLog.tsx`** (created): Fetches `/api/branch-log`, shows branch header, then for each entry renders `CheckpointRow` + log events using shared helpers from SessionDetail.

   - **`app/src/renderer/src/screens/SessionDetail.tsx`** (modified): Exported `logEventsToEvents`, `groupEvents`, `groupClaudeTurns`, `ClaudeTurnCard`, `CheckpointRow`, `DisplayItem`, `RenderItem` so BranchLog can reuse them.

   - **`app/src/renderer/src/screens/CheckpointDetail.tsx`** (rewritten): Now shows always-expanded detail view: header (checkpointId, branch badge, token count, file count), SummaryCard if available, diff via `fetchCheckpointDiff` + diff2html. No longer calls the missing `/api/checkpoints/:id/messages`.

   - **`app/src/renderer/src/components/SessionRow.tsx`** (modified): Added `repo: 130` to `COL_WIDTHS`, added Repo cell between User and Branch.

